originalText.text: Camille is a professional and talented photographer, whose creative vision yields the most beautiful images.  I had the pleasure of working with her for my 8 month maternity shoot.  She made me feel comfortable and confident.  She gave great instruction, and she took her time capturing various poses with precision.  The proof is in the final product, as I am incredibly pleased with how the images turned out.  I am thankful for the opportunity to work with Camille, and look forward to following her work for years to come!!

originalText.text: I had the most wonderful experience taking my maternity photos with Camille! Not only is she professional and artistic, but she is friendly and great to talk with in between photos. She really sets you at ease and makes you so comfortable so you can get the best photos possible. Being pregnant was such a special time in my life and it was so important to me to document it. The photos from my shoot with Camille are more beautiful and unique than I ever could have hoped! I highly recommend working with Camille for your milestone family photos- you will not be disappointed!

originalText.text: I cannot say enough good things about my experience with Camille!  I am not what you would call a "natural" in front of the camera and was nervous my maternity photos would be awkward. Camille was amazing and gave me and my husband lots of direction (and the client closet was fabulous) to get INCREDIBLE portraits of this really special time in our lives :) She was so warm and friendly that I didn't end up feeling awkward at all and am in absolute love with my photos!

originalText.text:
If you manage my strong dad tearing up after seeing the result of the photo shoot, you can definitely say Camille is a professional!

The photo shoot was lots of fun. When we entered the beautiful studio, it felt like home. The girls were relaxed from the start. Camille has a playful and fun way of giving the kids instructions for the different poses.

And it worked out perfectly. The result is amazing!!!!! You see the emotion and she was capable of capturing each unique personality of my kids in a beautiful way.

So if you ever look for a professional and fun photo shoot. I recommend Camille CD Photography!
